## 2. Diagrammatic Relationship Flow

```mermaid
erDiagram
    Users ||--|| Doctors : "1 : 1 (User has Doctor profile)"
    Users ||--o{ Addresses : "1 : N (User has addresses)"
    Roles ||--o{ Users : "1 : N (Role has users)"
    Users ||--o{ UserPatients : "1 : N (Account shares patient profiles)"
    Patients ||--o{ UserPatients : "1 : N (Profile shared with accounts)"
    Doctors ||--o{ Appointments : "1 : N (Doctor receives appointments)"
    Patients ||--o{ Appointments : "1 : N (Patient registers appointments)"
    Doctors ||--o{ DoctorSchedules : "1 : N (Doctor manages schedules)"
    Doctors ||--o{ DoctorDocuments : "1 : N (Doctor uploads documents)"
    Specializations ||--o{ Doctors : "1 : N (Specialization maps doctors)"
```

